// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-2781 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 5035edaa-5d1a-5423-9c48-adf28fa7d49b

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:8*" or process.executable like~ "*ubuntu:15.10*")
